khan]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Russian Professional Football League]]|url=http://www.pfl-russia.com/competitions/season-2015-2016/south/matchprotocol.php?match=3.0001|title=Game Report|date=19 July 2015}}</ref>\n\nHe made his debut for the [[FC Rostov]] main squad on 21 September 2016 in a [[Russian Cup (football)|Russian Cup]] game against [[FC Dynamo Moscow]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Russian Football National League]]|url=http://1fnl.ru/champioship/results/484/485/526/3349/#tab=game-info|title=Dynamo Moscow-Rostov game report|date=21 September 2016}}</ref>\n \n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Sportbox.ru|Futbol/Roman_Aleksandrovich_Khodunov_Futbol_28031997}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Khodunov, Roman}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:FC SKA Rostov-on-Don players]]\n[[Category:FC Rostov players]]\n[[Category:FC Krasnodar players]]\n\n\n{{Russia-footy-midfielder-1997-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Eastern Slavic name|Aleksandrovich|Khodunov}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| image = Roman Khodunov 2016.jpg\n| caption = Khodunov with Rostov in 2016\n| name = Roman Khodunov\n| fullname = Roman Aleksandrovich Khodunov\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1997|03|28|df=yes}}\n| height = {{height|m=1.83}}\n| position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]/[[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[FC Biolog-Novokubansk]]\n| clubnumber = 97\n| years1 = 2012\u20132015 | clubs1 = Donenergo Aksay                                                        | caps1 =    | goals1 = \n| years2 = 2015      | clubs2 = [[FC SKA Rostov-on-Don|SKA Rostov-on-Don]]                             | caps2 = 14 | goals2 = 1\n| years3 = 2016\u20132017 | clubs3 = [[FC Rostov]]                                                          | caps3 =  0 | goals3 = 0\n| years4 = 2017\u20132018 | clubs4 = [[FC Akademiya Futbola Rostov-on-Don|Akademiya Futbola Rostov-on-Don]] | caps4 =