ginal broadcast)\n| audio_format   = [[Monaural|Mono]]\n| first_aired    = 15 September 2010\n| last_aired     = 2 September 2011\n| preceded_by    = [[Ithin Eeta Passe]]\n| followed_by    = [[Sihina Piyapath]]\n| runtime        = Monday to Friday at 8:30pm\n| country        = [[Sri Lanka]]\n| language       = [[Sinhala language|Sinhala]]\n| website        = http://www.v2.itn.lk/?p=342\n| website_title  = Official website {{in lang|en}}\n}}\n'''''Bonda Meedum''''' ([[Sinhala language|Sinhala]]: \u0db6\u0ddc\u0db3 \u0db8\u0dd3\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca) is a [[Sri Lanka]]n television drama based on [[Bonda Meedum]], a popular series of novels created by Sri Lankan writer Sujeewa Prasanna Arachchi. The series debuted on 15 September 2010 and concluded on 2 September 2011. [[Independent Television Network]] was the official broadcaster for Bonda Meedum. Screening at the 8.30 pm slot, the teledrama exceeded even the popularity of the novels. [[Udari Warnakulasooriya]] and [[Saranga Disasekara]] were awarded most popular female and male actors of the year, respectively, at the 16th Sumathi Tele Awards 2011.<ref name=awards>{{cite web |url=http://www.thurunu.com/2011/11/23/16th-sumathi-tele-awards-2011/ |title=16th Sumathi Tele Awards 2011 &#124; Thurunu.com Unlimited Entertainment World |publisher=Thurunu.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120514025902/http://www.thurunu.com/2011/11/23/16th-sumathi-tele-awards-2011/ |archive-date=14 May 2012 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n==Story==\n{{copyedit |date=April 2020}}\nDhanuka([[Saranga Disasekara]]) is a handsome boy in his early twenties. He lives in [[Matale]] with his parents and sister. Due to their poverty, at the end of his school education he comes to [[Colombo]]. His father sends him to Senarath Maliyadde in order to get a job in his company. Senarath Maliyadde([[Buddhadasa Vithanarachchi]]) who lives in [[Nawala]] is a rich businessman and also a good friend of Dhanuka's father.\n\nSansala([[Udari Warnakulasooriya]]), Maliyadde's only daughter, is a beautiful proud girl in her late teenage. She just has her father and younger brother named Kasun. She received a marriage proposal from her aunt's son Saliya. She show little interest in Saliya. She spends her life happily but is sometimes maudlin about the death of her mother.\n\nAfter a long and arduous journey, Dhanuka arrives unheralded at Maliyadde's home.  Sansala opens the door to him and, considering him a perfect stranger, starts to question and blame him.  Dhanuka falls for her instantly. Maliyadde being out at the time and brother and sister knowing nothing of him, they leave Dhanuka at the gate notwithstanding a heavy downpour and he and his belongings are soaked. Maliyadde returns home in his car, spots Dhanuka by the gate and welcomes him in. So the tale begins.However Sansala and Dhanuka get married blessings with both families.But Unfortunately,Sansala falls into a coma and she send to India for treatments for a year.So,Dhanuka has to live without his wife.However,Sansala recovers from coma after a year.Finally,They lived happily.\n\n==Cast and characters==\n*[[Udari Warnakulasooriya]] as Sansala Rambukwella(nee`Maliyadda),Dhanuka's wife,Maliyadda's daughter,Dharmasena and Vimalas' daughter in-law.\n*[[Saranga Disasekara]] as Dhanuka Rambukwella,Dharmasena and Vimalas' son,Sansala's husband,Maliyadda's son in-law,Iroshani's brother.\n*Gayan Wickramathilaka as Saliya,Douglas and Charuni's son,Sansala and Kasuns' cousin brother,He loved Sansala for property.\n*[[Buddhadasa Vithanarachchi]] as Senarath Maliyadda,Sansala and Kasuns' father,Dhanuka's father in-law.\n*[[Janak Premalal]] as Dharmasena Rambukwella,Dhanuka and Iroshanis' father,Sansal's father in-law.\n*Madhani Malwaththa as Vimala Rambukwella,Dhanuka and Iroshanis' mother,Sansal's mother in-law.\n*Meena Kumari as Charuni,Maliyadda's sister,Saliya's mother,Sansala and Kasuns' paternal aunt.\n*[[Uddika Premarathna]] as Senaka,Dhanuka's best friend in his first job.\n*Thishuna Perera as Kasun Maliyadda,Sansala's younger brother.\n*[[Rajitha Hiran]] as Kumara, Male servant in Maliyadda house.\n*Gayana Sudharshani as Kamala, Female servant in Maliyadda house.\n*[[Ananda Wickramage]] as Douglas,Charuni's husband,Maliyadda's brother in-law,Saliya's father.\n*Piyumi Purasinghe as Iroshani Rambukwella,Dharmasena and Vimalas' daughter,Dhanuka's younger sister,Sansala's sister in-law.\n*[[Gihan Fernando]] as Palawaththe Victor \n*[[Gayesha Perera]] as Minoli\n*Sada Mihiri Amrasingha as Mayumi\n\n==Music==\n*Theme Song (By Amila Nadeeshani and Surendra Perera): [[Sinhala language|Sinhala]]: \u0db6\u0ddc\u0db3 \u0db8\u0dd3\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\n\n==Awards==\n* The most popular actress of the year (16th Sumathi Tele Awards 2011):<ref name=awards /> Udari Warnakulasuriya (Bonda Meedum)\n* The most popular actor of the year (16th Sumathi Tele Awards 2011):<ref name=awards /> Saranga Disasekara (Bonda Meedum)\n\n==Slogan==\n* [[Sinhala language|Sinhala]]: \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca - \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca \u0d94\u0db6\u0dda \u0d86\u0daf\u0dbb\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd2...\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20130623232129/http://www.v2.itn.lk/?p=342 Official website] {{in lang|en}}\n* [http://srineth.com/?nav=more&cat=184 Aadara desak] Udari Warnakulasuriya's Sinhala Teledrama all episodes on [http://srineth.com/?nav=more&cat=184 lakbima] tv\n* Boda Meedum Actress Udari Warnakulasuriya's latest teledrama '[http://www.srineth.com/watch/?v=4778fa14146 Sayuri]' on [http://www.srineth.com/watch/?v=4778fa14146 tharunaya] watch all episodes.\n\n[[Category:Sri Lankan television shows]]\n[[Category:Sri Lankan drama television series]]\n[[Category:2010 Sri Lankan television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2011 Sri Lankan television series endings]]